definitions.definition: Consisting of, relating to or contained between two plane surfaces.
Having wings that form a dihedral angle, especially when the angle between the upper sides is less than 180°.
labels: of a kite or an aeroplane
definitions.label_groups: of a kite or an aeroplane

definitions.definition: Of wing pairs, inclined at an upward angle to each other.
